<div class="container-fluid bg-2 text-center">
  <h3>About Soren <em>'Bjergsen'</em> Bjerg</h3>
  <li><strong>Bjergsen started his career in June 2012 where he played for Team LDLC.</li>
  <li>In October 2012 he joined the team 'Copenhagan Wolves' who were then rebranded to 'Ninjas in Pyjamas' in May 2013.</li>
  <li>He stayed with Ninjas in Pyjamas until November 2013.</li>
  <li>Bjergsen is now currently the mid laner for Team SoloMid.</strong></li>
 
